All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AdminApp
[Admin Module] Admin Starter App containing list of Admin Functions.
AppHelper
Abstract helper class for various modules to inherit to display their UI interface and allow returning to the previous 'page' the user was on.
Booking
Represents a movie booking.
Cinema
Represents a cinema hall located at a particular cineplex.
CinemaClass
Represents a group of constants related to the type of available cinema classes.
Cineplex
Represents a cineplex outlet.
CineplexApp
[Admin Module] Cineplex App under Configure System Settings.
ContentRating
Represents a group of constants related to the movie content ratings.
DayType
Represents a group of constants related to the type of days in a week.
FileReader
Helper class to perform CRUD functions on .txt files.
Holiday
Represents a public holiday.
HolidayApp
[Admin Module] Holiday App under Configure System Settings.
HolidayHelper
Helper class to retrieve data in the holidays .txt file.
LoginApp
[Admin Module] Login App for users to enter their credentials to use the admin system.
MainMenu
 
Movie
Represents a movie listing.
MovieBooking
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie Booking App to create a new booking.
MovieGenre
Represents a group of constants related to the different movie genres available.
MovieGoerCheckBooking
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie Booking History App to check booking history.
MovieGoerMenu
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie-Goer Starter App containing list of Movie-Goer Functions.
MovieHelper
Helper class to display top 5 movie listings based on Ticket Sales or Review Ratings
MovieListingApp
[Admin Module] Movie Listing App containing CRUD functions for Movies.
MovieRate
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie Rating App to rate and review a movie.
MovieType
Represents a group of constants related to the type of movie (i.e., 2D, 3D).
MovieView
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie App to view movie listings.
MovieViewBooking
[Movie-Goer Module] Movie Booking App to create a new booking.
Review
Represents a movie review made by a movie-goer.
Seat
Represents a cinema seat.
Serializer
Helper class to Serialise (Write) and Deserialise (Read) objects into/from .dat files.
SettingApp
[Admin Module] Configure Settings App.
ShowingStatus
Represents a group of constants related to the showing status of a movie (i.e., Coming Soon, Now Showing).
ShowTime
Represents a movie showtime.
ShowtimeApp
[Admin Module] Showtime App containing CRUD functions for Movie ShowTimes.
ShowTimeStatus
Represents a group of constants related to the status of a showtime (i.e., Available, Sold Out).
Ticket
Represents a movie ticket.
TicketPricingApp
[Admin Module] Ticket Pricing App to control the modifiers affecting ticket prices (i.e., movie type, cinema class, etc.).
TicketType
Represents a group of constants related to the age of the movie-goer purchasing a ticket (i.e., Standard/Adult, Senior, Student).
TopFiveApp
[Admin Module] Top-Five App to configure settings to allow movie-goers to list top 5 movie listings based on filter (i.e., ticket sales, review ratings).
